OL,6,FComplaints about energy firms have
OL,7,Fsoared by 50 per cent in the past two
OL,8,Fyears, it has emerged.
OL,10,FMore than 100,000 complaints were
OL,11,Freceived by the Energy Ombudsman in
OL,12,F2022 with the main issues including
OL,13,Fincorrect billing, poor customer
OL,14,Fservice and problems switching
OL,15,Fsuppliers, according to the BBC.
OL,17,FThree-quarters of the cases heard were
OL,18,Fconcluded in the customer's favour, BBC
OL,19,FRadio 4's Money Box programme reported.
OL,3,CComplaints about energy firms soar by
OL,4,C50 per cent in two years
